data.description: Welcome to this hidden gem in the Southlake subdivision of Energy Corridor. Home features 3 beds, 2 bath with plenty of natural light. Pass the entertainers patio, as you walk into your home. This home offers open concept floor plan with a game room on the opposite side of the bedrooms and a secret room in the finished attic. Start saving on electricity, solar panels are paid off and home includes shutters in most of the windows! Conveniently located just minutes away from all the shopping and dining City Center and Memorial City Mall offer. Just a short ride to i10 and beltway 8. Come check it out!
